                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-801-18670819 t18670819-801-punishment-78"></join>Two Years' Imprisonment.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">OLD COURT.</hi>—<hi rend="italic">Friday, August</hi> 23<hi rend="italic">rd</hi>. 1867.</p>
